ingly continues on her roaring rampage of revenge against the band of assassins who had tried to kill her and her unborn child. She visits each of her former associates one-by-one, checking off the victims on her Death List Five until there's nothing left to do … but kill Bill.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"popularity":8.9459,"vote_count":14824,"poster_path":"/2yhg0mZQMhDyvUQ4rG1IZ4oIA8L.jpg","release_date":"2004-04-16","vote_average":7.876,"backdrop_path":"/pgG6tzJzC8mjGqhaT8IWwEk00xf.jpg","original_title":"Kill Bill: Vol. 2","original_language":"en"},{"id":400,"adult":false,"title":"Things to Do in Denver When You're Dead","video":false,"overview":"Five different criminals face imminent death after botching a job quite badly.","genre_ids":[18,80],"popularity":1.6628,"vote_count":418,"poster_path":"/3LxYzYybOVpnw0juCSlNL5cj8NK.jpg","release_date":"1995-12-01","vote_average":6.453,"backdrop_path":"/J4l8AvrK8ByAjnoKposMLh3ubL.jpg","original_title":"Things to Do in Denver When You're Dead","original_language":"en"},{"id":479,"adult":false,"title":"Shaft","video":false,"overview":"New York police detective John Shaft arrests Walter Wade Jr. for a racially motivated slaying. But the only eyewitness disappears, and Wade jumps bail for Switzerland. Two years later Wade returns to face trial, confident his money and influence will get him acquitted -- especially since he's paid a drug kingpin to kill the witness.","genre_ids":[28,12,80,53],"popularity":2.35,"vote_count":1403,"poster_path":"/5ncvnNPaN73cOqD4muE413sSOyY.jpg","release_date":"2000-06-15","vote_average":6.007,"backdrop_path":"/sblTwYXpm6Nrl4qewg3526lBdlK.jpg","original_title":"Shaft","original_language":"en"},{"id":271825,"adult":false,"title":"Billa","video":false,"overview":"Billa, a powerful outlaw with a long list of enemies, kills Rajesh, a member of his gang, after he quits the criminal life. But Rajesh's fiancee and his sister pledge to take revenge on Billa.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"popularity":0.7059,"vote_